lead_paragraph: A chart on Monday listing the National Football League’s final leaders in seven categories included, in some editions, outdated statistics for three players, one each in touchdowns, tackles and interceptions; in some copies, it also omitted two quarterbacks from the passing yards list. A corrected chart can be found at nytimes.com/sports.
